# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:17
translate chinese jezs9_a35a7040:

    # det "Honestly? It's wonderful."
    det "说实话？这感觉真棒。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:19
translate chinese jezs9_7524850c:

    # det "Sure, it's hard and it'll probably get harder as he gets older and becomes a teenager..."
    det "当然，这不容易，而且随着他长大变成青少年，情况可能会越来越难……"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:20
translate chinese jezs9_54622736:

    # det "but every time I see that boy, I see a small version of myself."
    det "但每次看到那个小家伙，我仿佛都看到了自己缩小版。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:22
translate chinese jezs9_f4f30712:

    # det "He's a piece of me. It's like I ripped my heart out of my chest and it grew a new body and started walking around."
    det "他是我的一部分。就像我把心从胸膛里掏出来，它长出了新的躯体，开始在世间行走。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:23
translate chinese jezs9_8f2b4168:

    # det "Every time I see him, I'm like \"I made that!\""
    det "每次见到他，我都会感叹：“这是我创造的！”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:24
translate chinese jezs9_4da143de:

    # det "And he looks at me the same way. His little eyes so full of love."
    det "而他也用同样的眼神看着我。那双小眼睛里满是爱意。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:25
translate chinese jezs9_dca2579a:

    # det "He's my best friend. My little buddy."
    det "他是我的挚友。我的小伙伴。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:26
translate chinese jezs9_db85ba7b:

    # det "I'm so ridiculously proud of him. I can't image loving anything as much as I love him."
    det "我为他感到无比自豪。我无法想象还有什么能让我像爱他一样深爱。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:27
translate chinese jezs9_fb777db1:

    # pc "That's beautiful. Do you ever wish you had somebody to help you though?"
    pc "这真美。不过，你有没有希望有人能帮你分担一下呢？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:29
translate chinese jezs9_9e011005:

    # det "Sometimes. Although part of me likes having him all to myself."
    det "有时候。虽然我内心的一部分也喜欢独占他。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:31
translate chinese jezs9_a414f5fc:

    # det "But my mom helps a lot. It would be so much tougher if I didn't have her here to watch him while I'm working."
    det "但我妈妈帮了大忙。如果工作时没有她在这里照看他，我会难得多。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:33
translate chinese jezs9_5aef971d:

    # det "She's amazing. Also a single mother."
    det "她太棒了。也是个单亲妈妈。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:34
translate chinese jezs9_32518ec0:

    # pc "That's awesome. I'm glad you all have each other."
    pc "真了不起。很高兴你们彼此都有依靠。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:35
translate chinese jezs9_cbe5cec8:

    # det "Yeah, me too."
    det "是啊，我也是。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs9.rpy:2
    old "To unlock this conversation, you have to spend the night at Jez's house and meet her family."
    new "要解锁这段对话，你得在杰兹家过夜并见见她的家人。"

